id: pm-ph3i
title: Windows packed-extension install regression exceeds the generic Vitest timeout
description: "PR #573 Windows regression run 29511033166 job 87664537351 failed only because the real packed npm extension installation test exceeded Vitest's generic 30-second timeout (about 36.2 seconds). The operation itself completed; the test needs an explicit install-aware timeout that preserves the real end-to-end assertion. Duplicate-safe all-status searches reviewed closed Windows/npm lineage pm-xaib, pm-2kkl, pm-gf6f, pm-arax, and pm-0fhw; those items describe completed historical failures, not this current timing regression."
type: Issue
