author: codex-gpt5-root
acceptance_criteria: The packed-extension install integration test passes on Windows Node 24 without weakening its real npm-install assertions; focused local test and the hosted Windows regression job pass
parent: pm-doxj
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: fixed
expected_result: Packed-extension install regression passes on hosted Windows Node 24 with all real npm-install assertions intact.
actual_result: "PR #573 head 8ee7756723b7565e77f83ccb3803849f50f89db9 Windows regression run 29514695379 job 87676853924 passed in 1m43s; full local corpus passed 292 files and 5,746 tests at exact 100/100/100/100 coverage."
