comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T15:43:46.896Z",codex-gpt5-root,"Implementation evidence: the failing hosted run completed the underlying npm work but exceeded Vitest's generic 30-second ceiling at about 36.2 seconds. The existing real pack/install/doctor assertions are unchanged; only this integration test now declares a 60-second external-install budget. Focused execution passes locally in 1.48 seconds."
  "2026-07-16T15:58:41.470Z",codex-gpt5-root,"Full-corpus proof: all 292 files / 5,746 tests pass at exact 100/100/100/100 with the real packed npm extension test preserved and included. Hosted Windows confirmation remains pending on the next PR head, so this issue remains actively in progress."
  "2026-07-16T16:28:17.615Z",codex-gpt5-root,"Hosted acceptance evidence: PR #573 head 8ee7756723b7565e77f83ccb3803849f50f89db9 Windows regression run 29514695379 job 87676853924 passed in 1m43s, including the unchanged real packed npm extension install assertions under the explicit 60-second test budget. The subsequent source-only analyzer remediation also passes the complete local corpus: 292 files / 5,746 tests / exact 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
